des:
Stay Sharp is a an engaging collection of daily activities: Every day, you will have a new daily focus and a new type of exercise. These activities have no age limit , Stay sharp with each daily focus (Memory, Happiness, Relaxation …) and while exploring each daily exercise (Math, Logic, Yoga …)

Stay Sharp was designed by specialists to challenge and enhance cognitive performances and it’s especially targeted to the demographic of adults 55 years of age and older
